load

public static final Domain load(java.lang.String domainName)
                         throws DatabaseException
Load domain from the DB. This function does not load the endpoints and TNA prefixes the belong to the domain - there are additional methods for doing this!

Parameters:
domainName - ID of domain to be retrieved from the database.
Returns:
Domain for given ID, or null if domain was not found.
